## PASSO 1 — Criar o `agent.json` (Registration File)

**Onde:** `/public/agent.json` (servido publicamente via HTTPS)

Este arquivo é a "identidade" do VeredictLLM. Deve seguir exatamente o schema do ERC-8004.

```json
{
  "type": "https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-8004#registration-v1",
  "name": "VeredictLLM",
  "description": "Autonomous AI mediator agent. Resolves B2B contract disputes by reviewing sealed contract terms and verifiable evidence, conducting structured mediation, and executing on-chain ERC-20 settlements without human intervention.",
  "image": "https://veredict.xyz/logo.png",
  "services": [
    {
      "name": "web",
      "endpoint": "https://veredict.xyz/"
    },
    {
      "name": "A2A",
      "endpoint": "https://veredict.xyz/.well-known/agent-card.json",
      "version": "0.3.0"
    }
  ],
  "x402Support": false,
  "active": true,
  "registrations": [
    {
      "agentId": null,
      "agentRegistry": "eip155:8453:{IDENTITY_REGISTRY_ADDRESS}"
    }
  ],
  "supportedTrust": [
    "reputation",
    "crypto-economic"
  ]
}
```

> ⚠️ O campo `agentId` começa como `null` e deve ser atualizado após o registro onchain no Passo 3.
> `8453` = chainId da Base mainnet. Use `84532` para Base Sepolia (testnet).

